---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact & Support"
  description="Contact and support for Digital Compass (compass.madeinro.eu) and its MCP endpoint."
>
  <article class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h1>Contact &amp; Support</h1>
      <p><em>Contact și suport — răspundem în română sau engleză.</em></p>

      <h2>Operator</h2>
      <p>Digital Compass (compass.madeinro.eu) is operated by <strong>Marian Matinca</strong>, Romania.</p>

      <h2>Support</h2>
      <p>
        For any question about the guides, a correction, or the Digital Compass app for AI
        assistants (MCP endpoint), write to:
      </p>
      <p><a href="mailto:marian@mmatinca.eu"><strong>marian@mmatinca.eu</strong></a></p>
      <p>
        We usually reply within 2 business days. Corrections to reporting channels or procedures are
        prioritised — this content only works if it is accurate.
      </p>

      <h2>In an emergency</h2>
      <p>
        Do not wait for an email reply. If money or accounts are at immediate risk, follow the
        emergency steps in the relevant guide and use the official channels listed there
        (in Romania: DNSC call center <strong>1911</strong>, your bank's fraud line, Poliția
        Română). Într-o urgență nu aștepta un răspuns pe email — folosește canalele oficiale din
        ghidul relevant.
      </p>

      <h2>For developers &amp; AI agents</h2>
      <p>
        Machine-readable discovery:
        <a href="/.well-known/mcp.json">/.well-known/mcp.json</a> · sources and methodology:
        <a href="/surse">/surse</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
